ExitCode: 0
Stdout: ```
hello there
```
---
// Test: rc-string-replacefirst-no-leak
function main() returns ExitCode
	let s = "hello world"
	let result = s.replaceFirst("o", with: "0")
	print(result)
	return 0
end 'main'
---
ExitCode: 0
Stdout: ```
hell0 world
```
